Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術是將物質理解分解並且再構築的科學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是萬能的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不能從無中誕生物質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須付出相應的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是鍊金術的基本 等價交換
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師有一個禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人體鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是任何人都不能觸犯的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德他們遇到的男人——馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有一個不完整的賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被愛德的誠心所感動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可說出了隱藏研究資料的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理完機械鎧的愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到了有馬可研究資料的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國立中央圖書館第一分館前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可的研究資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太麻煩了 所以把整個建築都燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央市都做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我剛剛說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之小弟發現馬可的資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊已經搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以回來看看東方之都的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:02:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉托尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有味道 有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散發著血之味道的伊修瓦爾人就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把那傢伙吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃得不剩一根頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}被隱藏的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從愛力克兄弟的事件以後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有人提供斯卡的情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是已經不在東方之都了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼也得讓他在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能把中央市沒處理好的事件解決的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這支股票也就漲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能利用的東西全都利用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我爬到大總統的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握了全部軍事權為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意一下不妥的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡量注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才傳來了馬魯河發生爆炸的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煤氣爆炸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近比較亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是斯卡穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的出血狀況這麼嚴重 應該不會安然無恙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 直到確認他死亡為止都不能放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈博克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶領你的部隊去清理那些瓦礫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要日以繼夜進行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要把那傢伙的屍體找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我們過勞死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不親眼見到那傢伙的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不能安心約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 下次再吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過搞得他那副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡一時半會也動不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再回趟中央市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把斯卡的事情報告給父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒得一點都不剩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是羅斯少尉和普羅修軍曹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部要求你出席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華·愛力克的護衛由我們接手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 本想總算能和悶熱的大叔說拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是護衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於圖書館的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人對於第一分館的資料非常精通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 已經離職了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺沒法期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐突地問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是穿著鎧甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 這是什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 好漂亮的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這書山是什 什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有人住著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝絲卡 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人被埋進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挖 快挖 快挖 快挖這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心把書山弄塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為就這麼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是謝絲卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾在第一分館的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一分館
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼美妙的發音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從出生就喜歡書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我決定在那裡就職的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是升天一般的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 忘記是在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是看書導致被解僱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓生病的媽媽進入更好的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本應該好好工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了讀書以外幹什麼都很遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡都找不到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我是廢人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社會的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是否知道提姆·馬可寫的研究書在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是手寫的 而且還亂七八糟地插進了分類不同的書架裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 果然是被完全燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很想讀那本研究書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是被燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書的內容我全都記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個 所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對讀過一次的書裡面的內容全都會記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點花時間 要全部抄出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·馬可寫的研究書之手抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為量有點多 所以花了5天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界上還有這麼厲害的人呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是馬可的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆·馬可著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的一千種菜譜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖一大勺 加水少量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是今日的一千種菜譜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊 這哪裡是重要文件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是照著記憶裡面的全抄下來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來完全是白跑了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和馬可寫的一字一句都完全一樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 帶上這些回中央圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在那裡的話 相關書籍也都很齊全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 謝禮 謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的登錄號碼和證明身份的銀懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我的年度研究費裡取出那些交給謝絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去大總統府的國家鍊金術師機關就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝絲卡 真的非常感謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從研究費…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼金額
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出手就是這個金額
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這料理書真的是鍊金術的研究書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術被惡意使用的話可是危險的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用暗號來書寫研究書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一般人看起來只是普通的料理研究
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的內容只有寫的人才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本非常難懂的鍊金術書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有本人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼解讀？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知識和靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就是靠毅力來鑽研
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了就要暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 有鴿子料理的項目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴿子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那難道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可能說的就是綠色的獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲學家的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉梅露的古老手抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者拉姆斯普林姆克寫的有關賢者之石的書拿來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 讓我們開始幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西 這該死的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 也許直接去問馬可先生比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 去問了就是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝絲卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親轉移到優秀的醫院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解讀有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳找到工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 多虧了你們兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個廢人也能給別人帶來幫助讓我感到很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是廢人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能對什麼事情全心全意這本身就是一種才能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳有很強的記憶力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從阿姆斯壯少佐那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 我不是說了你到中央市的話先來跟我打聲招呼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有急事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個休斯中佐在拉家常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個孩子到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近事件什麼的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔克的合成獸事件還沒有了結
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你想起痛苦的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就已經是很忙的時期了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一分館又全燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一分館？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的書庫裡保管著事件的記錄什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影響到業務真是麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人在找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實也讀過軍隊的刑事記錄 也記得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上辦手續
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡工資不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拿出自信努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 馬上工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大叔是人販子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能對什麼事情全心全意這本身就是一種才能嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真能說呢 弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著某處的某位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從心底這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個某處的某位就繼續全心全意地努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到閉館時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到今天就整整十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真能集中精神一直到閉館
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟吵架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算解不開也不用自暴自棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開了 暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯 這是惡魔的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可追求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會恨你的 馬可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石的材料是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為了精製一個石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要大量的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊在進行那種不人道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼能饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事能保密嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克兄弟今天也關在房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 飯也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是積累了疲勞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近精神太過集中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦解讀的資料內容是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也僅是回想起來就感覺全身不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃口飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了手能碰到的地方卻被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被抓住的東西踢飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來神是徹底地討厭觸犯禁忌的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都會這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事一直想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為太害怕而沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克兄弟 在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 開門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了 愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石居然隱藏了這種秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那種悶熱的男人逼問的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到軍隊幹了那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相有時確實殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可說的話 還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能看到真相中的另一個真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相中的另一個真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鍊金術的研究書一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面看到的只是真相的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 政府關聯的鍊金術研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央市裡有四處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中馬可氏所屬的是第三研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡最可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市內的研究所我全部都看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像沒有什麼重大研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個建築是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第五研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有塌方的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在禁止入內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼根據？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊就是監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石的材料是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 活人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監獄裡也有死刑犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外是說處刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…囚犯是材料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擺出那種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不願意那樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係到管轄不同的監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說政府也脫不了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:20:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺是要調查到不得了的事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 讓你們當作沒聽見的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也許會成為高度的政治問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試探一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 你們對這件事不要多問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克兄弟也要乖乖待著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們是準備潛入這個建築物調查內部吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想 沒想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未使用的建築卻配門衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼進去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個入口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會因為鍊成反應的光被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也封鎖得嚴嚴實實的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那巨大的身體沒法通過這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喜歡才變這麼大身體的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}（失落）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,66
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 48
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒來客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知死活的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像的還要窄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方如果是普通人的體型是無法通過的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體小真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己說自己小了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼現在沒有使用呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有對劍保有榮耀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有明白自己屬於異端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的住民們在狂笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血的刀刃在咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8話 第五研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥中追求快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生死極限中感受生命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報上你們的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:33.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}不必消去這份記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:35.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}人生不是還很漫長？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}那些沒有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:42.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:58.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}明明一直在追趕著夢的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:05.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}跌跌撞撞地走在彎曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:08.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不奢望回到那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}只是在苦尋那片丟失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像你明白一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:18.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}除去那像犧牲之後的悲傷表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:20.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}罪孽之後並不是淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:22.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}而是一直以來背負的苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:23.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}迷失在沒有出口的情感迷宮中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在等待著誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像在白色筆記本上刻畫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}很想誠實地說出心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在逃避什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…原來是叫做現實的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:35.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}為了實現願望而活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不禁想要大喊  你能聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:43.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}平安無事卻讓人沒法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…無家可歸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}感謝同伴們帶來的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以要更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}讓人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:57.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur6}這種痛苦也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:32.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的緋紅天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:38.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:44.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}約定和契約  被初夏的微風所懷抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:48.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}兩個人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:57.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在強顏歡笑的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:23:02.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}隱藏著逐漸擴大的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:11.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只裝做沒有發現  選擇了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:21.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌邊繼續等待那沒有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:29.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜裡  無法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:34.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}其實我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:40.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}那天看到的緋紅天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}總有一天會想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:51.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}抱著沒有實現的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:55.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}兩個人一起出發


